25a48f7a0d87","tid":516614,"uid":54760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T23:58:56.000Z","msg":"啱啱搵左<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />而家扑緊野"},{"pid":"187727b25b8e152d7cc3fcd2973ed373e7c283c6","tid":516614,"uid":87679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>真係好想搵 差啲就搵咗<br />\n但如果佢都掛住我 點解唔搵我呢？<br />\n算吧啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果佢都係咁諗呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好了解我<br />\n佢明知我唔係啲咁易放低嘅人<br />\n明知我仲掛住佢㗎<br />\n所以如果佢都有丁點掛住我 一早搵咗我了<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1f6dc090a26b8fd7c529a93137e8e367fb9a44","tid":516614,"uid":21058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T00:41:46.000Z","msg":"其實我一直都掛住你<br />\n2年啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad20be5ce821425ec5a3f6a06d2ac9720ba883b3","tid":516614,"uid":152386,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:49:34.000Z","msg":"我好掛住佢<br />\n我揾咗佢<br />\n但我知 佢無掛住我<br />\n係我犯賤<br />\n我一直都放唔低<br />\n半年喇 <br />\n明明無一齊到<br />\n但點解我會咁掛住你<br />\n我想放低你<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb5f75bce0ff51c89c95662b01caef4f5f7c9260","tid":516614,"uid":139814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-02T08:54:10.000Z","msg":"傻啦 唔會"},{"pid":"c123f1a27bd9ca2f03d7dd74ff052a46d12ef3d0","tid":516614,"uid":159512,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee246f60676f5cb64d696ebc7dcafb7744af3dcd","tid":516614,"uid":148348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"0154ac3b12a75617a1b2490490efe3032b2ba732","tid":516614,"uid":102096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:11:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"當日太蠢 唔識得珍惜<im